data.description:
Beautiful Toll Brothers home in Summerlin, Traccia community.  Prime location close to Downtown Summerlin and Red Rock Casino. This guard gated community, features 2 community pools, tennis courts, and resort-like amenities.  Home is zoned for the highly desired Palo Verde High School area.

This home features 3 bedrooms with a loft and rotunda sitting area.  Primary suite also has rotunda sitting area and balcony overlooking the well landscaped back yard.  There are 2 gas fireplaces, 8 foot round interior doors, french doors from family room, new shutters throughout, custom ceiling fans, walnut custom cabinets throughout, walk-in custom pantry, trash compactor, and new stair lift (can be removed by seller). New sink, oven/microwave combo, washer and dryer.  Home also has a 3-car, finished garage with storage and tile/hardwood throughout!  Too many amenities to list.  This home is a must see!
